Package: roistats
Title: Convienience functions for applying basic stats to sub-groups
Version: 0.1.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Yufei",
           family = "Zhao",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "fay.zz0213@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6511-8507"))
Description: The goal of this package is for easily applying same t-tests/basic data description across several sub-groups, with the output as a nice arranged data.frame. Multiple comparison and the significance symbols are also provided.
